<h1 style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333;">Hi All,</h1>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #555; line-height: 1.6;">
    Please note, there is a risk identifier in the <strong><%= @project.name %></strong> project by IT PM.
</p>

<table class="list issue-report" style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 20px 0;">
    <thead>
        <tr style="background-color: #f4f4f4; color: #333; font-weight: bold;">
            <th style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; text-align: left;">ID</th>
            <th style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; text-align: left;">Project Name</th>
            <th style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; text-align: left;">Subject</th>
            <th style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; text-align: left;">Impact</th>
            <th style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; text-align: left;">Tracker</th>
            <th style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; text-align: left;">Stakeholder/User</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        <% @issues.each do |issue| %>
        <tr style="background-color: <%= cycle('#ffffff', '#f9f9f9') %>; color: #555;">
            <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px;"><%= issue.id %></td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px;"><%= @project.name %></td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px;"><%= issue.subject %></td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px;"><%= issue.impact %></td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px;"><%= issue.tracker.name %></td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px;"><%= issue.stakeholder %></td>
        </tr>
        <% end %>
    </tbody>
</table>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #555; line-height: 1.6;">
    We will discuss the same in the upcoming IT Weekly meet.
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 20px 0 0; color: #555;">
    Regards, <br>
    <strong>PMO</strong>
</p>
<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #888;">nknkc</span>

<style>
    * {
        font-size: 14px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    table.list.issue-report {
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    table.list.issue-report th, table.list.issue-report td {
        text-align: left;
    }
</style>
